<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV31">
<l>icaimiṉkaḷ tūteṉ ṟicaittā licaiyila meṉṟalaimē</l>
<l>lacaimiṉka ḷeṉṟā lacaiyuṅko lāmampoṉ māmaṇikaḷ</l>
<l>ticaimiṉ miḷirun tiruvēṅ kaṭattuvaṉ ṟāṭcimayam</l>
<l>micaimiṉ miḷiriya pōvāṉ vaḻikkoṇṭa mēkaṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [I] speak “speak as [my] messengers!” there is no speaking. If [I] say</l>
<l>“move over my head!” will they move? Yes – the clouds that took the way</l>
<l>to go to Vēṅkaṭam where flashes gleam in [all] directions, – pretty gold</l>
<l>[and] big sapphires  – for lightning to gleam on the strong-footed summits.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
